OL,3,CScottish culture sector would thrive
OL,4,Cwith independence, minister to insist
OL,6,FIn the 10th paper of the Scottish
OL,7,FGovernment's pro-independence Building
OL,8,Fa New Scotland series, which will
OL,9,Flaunch on Friday, ministers argue the
OL,10,F"priceless assets" of the country's
OL,11,Fculture sector will lead to a
OL,12,F"successful independent nation".
OL,14,FMr Robertson is expected to outline
OL,15,Fhow EU membership will allow artists
OL,16,Fto move freely without requiring visas
OL,17,For custom requirements, making it
OL,18,Feasier for them to tour and exchange
OL,19,Fideas.
