OL,3,CScottish culture sector would thrive
OL,4,Cwith independence, minister to insist
OL,6,FThe minister will say: "Culture is one
OL,7,Fof Scotland's priceless assets and we
OL,8,Fare determined to protect and enhance
OL,9,Fit, putting it at the heart of our
OL,10,Fcommunities for the benefit of
OL,11,Feveryone.
OL,13,F"These strong foundations could help
OL,14,Fus become a successful, inclusive,
OL,15,Fvibrant independent nation.
OL,17,F"Our ambition is to rejoin the EU as a
OL,18,Fmember state in our own right as soon
OL,19,Fas possible.
