OL,3,CScottish culture sector would thrive
OL,4,Cwith independence, minister to insist
OL,6,F"This would mean regaining the immense
OL,7,Fbenefits of free movement of people
OL,8,Fand the networks that support the
OL,9,Fexchange of ideas upon which culture
OL,10,Fthrives.
OL,12,F"It is more important than ever that
OL,13,FScotland has the powers necessary to
OL,14,Fsupport and develop our cultural and
OL,15,Fcreative sectors: to ensure that
OL,16,Fcreative professionals can work and
OL,17,Fcollaborate with their peers around
OL,18,Fthe world and ensure that everyone in
OL,19,FScotland can fully benefit for our
OL,20,Frich and diverse culture."
